===Quotations===
'''2000''' "In the middle distance several '''foolhardy''' souls in wet suits were surfing toward some foamy outbursts on the rocky headland; nearer in, a scattering of paddlers was being continually and, it seemed, happily engulfed by explosive waves." &mdash; Bill Bryson, ''In a Sunburned Country'', p. 14